Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:04.11,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Zangetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.11,0:00:05.19,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Zangetsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:08.11,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:15.28,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.13,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:00.42,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Weren't we in a hurry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.88,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Something's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:03.56,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sign of the Cleaner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:05.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:08.10,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that Spiritual Pressure\Ntrain-like thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:09.32,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:13.26,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinarily, a Soul Reaper can't\Ndo anything about the Cleaner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:17.60,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,From the traces of Spiritual Pressure,\Nit appears Aizen did something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:32.00,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,What are you afraid of, Gin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:38.51,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Reason exists for those who\Nmust rely on it to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.35,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:43.81,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Towards the end of all reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.35,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Is it bad if that thing is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:52.69,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave things like this,\Nit's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:53.88,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.08,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:56.20,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:00.20,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,This Precipice World, as\Nthe name suggests,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:02.39,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,is a place isolated temporally\Nand spatially from
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:05.02,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,both the World of the Living\Nand the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:09.76,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,The Cleaner existed to keep\Nthose who entered
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:11.51,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,here from staying a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:14.97,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.66,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to teach\Nyou in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.39,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:27.39,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,The Final Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:29.84,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,The Final...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.56,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:49.16,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I sleeping here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.31,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,The Final...Getsugatensho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.11,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:20.93,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And this is where you could teach me?\NWhy's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.17,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,The Precipice World
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.96,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,is a rupture in space surrounded
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:30.54,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,by multiple layers of\Ntemporal torrents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:33.94,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.59,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to know\Nwhat it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.24,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Put simply,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:42.75,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,time flows at a much faster rate\Nthan in the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.49,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Expressed in numbers,\Nit's 2000 times as fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:48.20,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,In the time that a year\Npasses on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.18,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,2000 years will have passed\Nhere in the Precipice World.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:51.25,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:54.09,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, besides being\Nthe pathway to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:57.60,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,the World of the Living, this Precipice World\Nwas also used as an exile for criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:01.39,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the Restrictive Current\Nand the Cleaner exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.36,B2,ISSHIN (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the Restrictive Current\Ncaptures you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.53,B2,ISSHIN (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then you would be unable to escape\Nthe Precipice World and die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:12.05,B2,ISSHIN (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the Cleaner pursues you, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:14.48,B2,ISSHIN (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then you would be hurled\Nto a time greatly different {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.00,B2,ISSHIN (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}than the temporal coordinates at which\Nyou entered the Precipice World.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:20.38,B2,ISSHIN (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is why there was a\Nvariance of several days{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:24.99,B2,ISSHIN (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when you first entered the Soul Society\Nafter being pursued by the Cleaner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.29,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you have Urahara's\Ntechnical skills
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.37,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,to thank for getting off\Nwith only a few days
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.72,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,variance after the Cleaner\Npursued you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.86,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinarily, you would've been\Nhurled about a century
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.05,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,and died from your body\Nbeing unable to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:39.93,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,up with the sudden\Npassage of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.48,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,But right now,\Nthat Cleaner is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:49.27,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good opportunity\Nto gain some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.66,B2,ISSHIN (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flow of time within\Nthe Precipice World is {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:52.99,B2,ISSHIN (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}2000 times that\Nof the outside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:56.52,B2,ISSHIN (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words,\Neven if you trained 2000 hours here, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:59.00,B2,ISSHIN (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}only one hour will have\Ngone by on the outside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:03.79,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,There is no means of sealing the\NCleaner in the Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:06.04,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,but there is a way to stop\Nthe Restrictive Current.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:16.81,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,We call it Realm Fixation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.27,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Normally,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.12,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,it's done by having a group of\Nlow-ranking Soul Reapers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:24.69,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,pool their Spiritual Pressure to\Nfixate the Restrictive Current.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.28,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,But I can perform it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.70,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I will hold down the\NRestrictive Current
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.62,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,until my Spiritual Pressure\Nis exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:36.04,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,By my rough estimate,\Nthat'll be 2000 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:38.78,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Or about 3 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.13,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Use that time to get an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:43.97,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:44.88,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:46.78,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,You need to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:48.96,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Get your sword, Zangetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:51.43,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,to tell you about the\NFinal Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.91,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What...What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.28,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:13.78,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's asleep\Non the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:15.95,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,All the cars and traffic\Nlights have stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.76,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,This is not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:20.24,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it look like the world\Nhas come to an end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.43,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:22.85,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And it isn't a movie, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:23.96,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.68,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't anybody awake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.47,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:28.02,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:28.59,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.67,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.55,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me here alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.47,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.61,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:39.14,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:41.18,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Arisawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:44.25,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.47,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to see someone,\Neven if it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.71,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... Did you take\Na look around?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.65,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's all sound asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.04,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I was getting lonely,\Nthinking maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:58.18,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only one still\Nawake in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:07:59.95,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, no one's waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.77,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so real and\Ncreepy, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:05.60,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I would've been able to handle\Nall this if it was just me here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:07.04,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,but this is way too freaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.71,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,But I sure am glad you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:12.36,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:15.07,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I'd rather you\Nworried about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:16.37,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, have you\Nseen Mizuiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:17.35,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.54,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.52,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you lariat me, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.52,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:27.31,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.68,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you dodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.64,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:41.79,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't dodge,\Nit's gonna hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.41,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you dodged my fist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.53,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,means you aren't putting your\Nsoul into your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:47.79,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:51.39,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you even know how to talk\Nwith your own Zanpakuto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:52.88,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:56.76,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never turned to Old Man Zangetsu\Noutside of battle like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:59.73,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Place your sword on your\Nlap and meditate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:02.00,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate your soul\Non only your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:02.77,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.12,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I get that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.28,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,That form is called Jinzen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.79,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,It is a form for carrying on a dialogue\Nwith one's Zanpakuto
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.61,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,that was devised over the course
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:41.43,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,of thousands of years since the\Nbeginning of the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:46.56,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, up until now,\Nall your techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.57,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,were acquired through\Nbrute force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:53.58,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:56.33,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,For you to progress further,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:59.28,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,you must venture into\Nrealms of millennia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.75,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,you never touched on before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.80,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Go...Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:15.66,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.66,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:20.57,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm by myself,\Nand everyone's asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:24.97,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,and I was lonely, and it was so quiet,\Nand no one's awake, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:27.11,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And then I got hyper, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.20,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Will you stop with the\Nnoisy excuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:30.72,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.34,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.34,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm serious. I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.34,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Honsho! Ogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.73,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:42.32,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'm taking\Nthem to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.97,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Can you carry Chizuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:44.99,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:46.80,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Up you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:49.85,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You better not touch her butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:50.87,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:54.81,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Arisawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:55.83,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:59.26,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Honsho's got bigger boobs\Nthan I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:07.72,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Here's what I know so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:11.53,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I went to take a look\Naround earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:13.31,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,but the town was cut off\Nright at the outskirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.65,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,There were only mountains\Npast that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:24.38,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe, but the entire\Ntown has been moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:29.08,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Ichigo has something\Nto do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:32.54,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?\NWho else is there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:34.53,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:39.29,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,If it was Ichigo's fault,\Nthen Ichigo is going to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.33,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of guy he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:49.53,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:52.82,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,A sight unfitting for\Nthe Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:56.29,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last we'll see of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:29.51,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:33.13,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,How unsightly of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:34.98,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:39.90,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:42.81,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.11,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Zangetsu is the only\None who should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:54.58,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,Is that any way to talk to the person\Nwho taught you how to breathe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:03.17,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Tensa Zangetsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:11.47,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,I can't blame you for\Nnot recognizing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:17.02,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time you've come\Nhere in a Bankai state.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.33,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.06,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Zangetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:27.03,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Zangetsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:27.88,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:30.74,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,What do you call your Bankai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:35.79,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,I am Tensa Zangetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:49.00,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,You've entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.28,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.69,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,This time, Zangetsu will\Nnot go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.76,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same with\Nmy Engetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:06.78,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Our Zanpakutos don't want\Nto teach us this technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:11.74,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,You'll learn why soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:23.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Old Man... I mean, you're\Nnot old right now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:25.51,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Zangetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.73,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'm not here to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:30.59,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I just need an answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:34.56,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,Answer? You mean about\Nthe Final Getsugatensho?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:36.45,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.14,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So you can hear what's\Nsaid outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:43.77,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:47.15,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,I can't teach you such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:48.64,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:52.43,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I need\Nyou to teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.15,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:15:01.00,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of what you want to protect\Nis none of my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.25,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.09,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:17.31,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,What you want to protect is\Nnot what I want to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:22.73,B2,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,My head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:25.09,B2,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.73,B2,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,The trains aren't running.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:30.20,B2,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get to the office,\Nor even go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.91,B2,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.47,B2,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad someone is awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:37.16,B2,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea\Nof what is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:38.58,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:48.00,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,A human with no awareness\Nof Spiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.01,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,is unable to sense my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:54.50,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,But their body can't withstand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:04.83,B2,GIN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Those kids over there\Nseem to be awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.94,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I recall seeing them\Nthrough Ulquiorra's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.62,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,They are Ichigo Kurosaki's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:30.61,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.42,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:35.21,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,"The fate of what you want to protect\Nis none of my concern."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:43.14,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking what you\Nmeant by that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.43,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you lent me your\Npower to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:53.07,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Was I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you lend me\Nyour power all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:58.04,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What were you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:00.97,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Zangetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:08.29,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly as I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:09.51,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:13.09,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:20.61,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,This world of yours used to be filled\Nwith skyscrapers, full of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:25.27,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,Now it has sunken low to look like\Nthe small town that's dear to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:34.49,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,The rain that continued to fall\Non this world has subsided,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.35,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,but in its place, everything\Nhas sunk into this ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:43.24,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,This all happened, Ichigo, because you\Nlost hope and stopped moving forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.35,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:58.36,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot leave you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:03.26,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,I will drag out the root of your\Ndespair right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:32.38,B2,WHITE ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:35.59,B2,WHITE ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.76,B2,WHITE ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:45.10,B2,WHITE ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.10,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:57.86,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.99,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to\Nlook for Kojima?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.00,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:03.91,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I did try looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:08.75,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since Ichigo disappeared,\Nhe's been going to school on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.32,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And he hasn't answered\Nhis cell phone either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:12.42,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So he's probably still\Nasleep somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.15,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You two have been hanging\Nout since middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.93,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought you were\Nbest friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:21.88,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's not like that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:26.26,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,We have our personal spaces.\NPeople need that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:28.31,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:32.44,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo was the first person\NMizuiro ever opened up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.98,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,He tends to put up\Na wall very quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:39.44,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,so it makes me happy just to see\Nhim walk up to people on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.41,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop this. What am\NI saying, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.85,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You were telling cheesy stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:51.87,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:55.22,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, after we drop off Chizuru\Nand Michiru at the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.22,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,go and find Kojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.61,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kunieda and Natsui?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:02.43,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Those two can manage\Nby themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.85,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look for Yuzu and Karin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.33,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't their Dad with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:10.78,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's probably unconscious\Nwith the rest of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:18.52,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:20.12,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,A-Arisawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:21.27,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.70,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.20,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to\Nworry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.04,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Who are those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:41.40,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Arisawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:43.85,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:49.06,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You're this close to me, yet you are\Nstill able to maintain your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:53.18,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Who...are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:58.05,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki will show\Nup here for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:01.43,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,With new powers, no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:06.33,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I want to bring those powers\Ncloser to perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:10.53,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Your deaths will help that cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.81,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Asano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.54,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:20.57,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.67,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Or is there something\Nyou can do here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.64,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother chasing after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:33.60,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start with this one first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:36.30,B2,TATSUKI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What'll I do? What'll I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.27,B2,TATSUKI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My body won't move.\NWhat'll I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:42.85,B2,TATSUKI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.47,0:23:22.64,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Arisawa, ever heard of a\Nmisattribution of arousal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:23.87,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you babbling about\Nat a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:25.67,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,When you're in an agitating situation\Nwith someone for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:28.43,B2,TENSA ZANGETSU,0000,0000,0000,,your brain misattributes\Nit as love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:30.88,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really? So you're in love\Nwith that freak in white.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:32.68,B2,TATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I told you to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:34.85,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,How did you come to\Nthat conclusion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:36.77,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to\NSoul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:38.10,B2,WHITE ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.35,0:23:41.00,B2,WHITE ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and return this place\Nto the way it used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.54,0:23:43.49,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't appear all\Nthat inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.49,0:23:44.49,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why not leave it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.49,0:23:45.56,B2,WHITE ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.31,0:23:48.94,B2,WHITE ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Everything mechanical\Nhas become unusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:51.36,B2,WHITE ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Once you fall asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:53.82,B2,WHITE ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,there's no telling where\Nyou'll end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.17,0:23:55.77,B2,WHITE ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried equipping myself\Nwith all sorts of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.77,0:23:56.97,B2,WHITE ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,but it's really a hassle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.97,0:23:58.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:04.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,He sure looks like\Nhe's having fun.